  "text": "More details about how the technology-enhanced tools framework was used in examining teacher beliefs are shared in the methodology, but first our conceptualization of science literacy that guided the development of the PD serving as a context for curriculum innovation, for this research, and for shaping the teacher orientation profiles is shared in Table 2 . Note: This science literacy conceptualization was developed by [CITATION_1] and as such is shared more concisely here.",
